We've added a recent publication which has received a lot of media coverage and which seems to validate Patricia Cornwell's theory.

In this article, there's a paragraph dedicated to Jack the Ripper. The addition of the recent French publication on the discovery of a painting depicting a presumed portrait of WALTER SICKERT is therefore entirely appropriate.
Full picture of the painting is preferable.
Important French publication and media sources regarding a new painting representing a portrait of Walter Sickert as Jack the Ripper by Jacques-Emile Blanche.
New publication on the alleged guilt of Walter Sickert. Important French media sources.
New French publication.
